Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.89,0:00:33.10,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}在悲傷中尋覓自我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.21,0:00:49.23,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}在淡波間追尋儚夢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.72,0:01:07.54,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}頓足向空深際蔚藍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.36,0:01:18.47,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}包容渺小自我  繼續向前邁進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.29,0:01:24.98,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}只望與你相見
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.01,0:01:30.70,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}唯有以笑比心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.76,0:01:35.87,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}只因有你相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.87,0:01:40.81,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}心中充滿光明
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.55,0:01:54.16,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}遙遙幽律逾破宙曉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.18,0:02:10.60,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}唯有醉情滿溢心間
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.89,0:00:33.10,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}悲しみに　試されるたび  少しずつ　強くなってく
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.21,0:00:49.23,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}ありふれた　毎日の中　夢のつづき　追いかけて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.72,0:01:07.54,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}歩きつかれて　見上げた空  深く　どこまでも　Blue
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.36,0:01:18.47,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}ちっぽけな自分　抱きしめて  それでも　進んでく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.29,0:01:24.98,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}あなたに会いたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.01,0:01:30.70,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}笑顔を伝えたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.76,0:01:35.87,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}あなたがいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.87,0:01:40.81,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}光が生まれるの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.55,0:01:54.16,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}遥かなる　優しい調べ  遠い宇宙　越えて届くの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.18,0:02:10.60,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2\fad(200,200)\be1}胸の奥　かけがえのない  甘い痛み  満ちていく
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,======================ED======================
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.11,0:24:06.98,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}黄昏に流れだした
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.16,0:24:10.68,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}制服の群れに
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.51,0:24:15.88,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}逆らうよに　自転車の
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.96,0:24:20.13,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}ペダル　思いきり踏んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.42,0:24:24.79,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}放課後のグランドの脇
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.85,0:24:28.27,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}金網をくぐって
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.33,0:24:33.68,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}去年　見つけた　ひまわりは
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.79,0:24:38.20,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}去年より　誇らしげに
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.23,0:24:41.67,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}空を見上げてた
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.46,0:24:47.00,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}折れないように　枯れないように
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.02,0:24:50.79,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}涙に出来たなら
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.41,0:24:57.71,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}明日は何かが変わるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.39,0:25:04.79,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}雨降る日は　雨に揺れる
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.80,0:25:09.23,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}あの　ひまわりみたいに
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.40,0:25:13.46,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}まっすぐ　背を伸ばして
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.70,0:25:20.38,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}今日は揺れていたって、いいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.11,0:24:06.98,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}黃昏下  逆行在流動的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.16,0:24:10.68,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}身著制服的人群中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.51,0:24:15.88,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}盡情地  蹬踩著
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.96,0:24:20.13,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}自行車的腳踏板
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.42,0:24:24.79,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}放學後  操場邊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.85,0:24:28.27,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}鑽過鐵絲網
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.33,0:24:33.68,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}去年發現的向日葵
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.79,0:24:38.20,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}比以往還要驕傲地
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.23,0:24:41.67,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}仰望著天空
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.46,0:24:47.00,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}不屈不撓  不會枯萎地
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.02,0:24:50.79,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}若是放聲哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.41,0:24:57.71,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}明天又會變得怎樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.39,0:25:04.79,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}下雨的日子  在雨中搖擺
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.80,0:25:09.23,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}就像那朵向日葵
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.40,0:25:13.46,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}挺直了腰杆
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.70,0:25:20.38,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(200,200)\be1}哪怕今日有所動搖  也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.63,0:00:17.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭已經開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.10,0:00:20.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是大家都沒有發覺而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.77,0:02:26.15,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(900,1000)\pos(460,370)\fs29}第三類近距離接觸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.34,0:02:25.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淺羽特派員
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.10,0:02:28.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這40天辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.46,0:02:31.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…謝謝  辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.16,0:02:33.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那麼明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.87,0:02:48.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天暑假就結束了…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.95,0:04:04.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.51,0:04:30.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.44,0:04:32.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腳  腳能夠到的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.79,0:05:02.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼻血…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.47,0:05:04.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.06,0:05:15.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.34,0:05:19.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你生病了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.69,0:05:25.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.99,0:05:26.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.10,0:05:27.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.16,0:05:28.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是姓？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.26,0:05:30.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野  加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.28,0:05:34.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會游泳嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.68,0:05:38.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.54,0:05:44.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會游泳嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.40,0:05:46.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.75,0:05:49.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不嫌棄的話  我教你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.92,0:05:52.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游泳的…方法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.97,0:05:54.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不樂意的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.80,0:06:17.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來我會拉著你的手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.56,0:06:19.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.29,0:06:36.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會痛的  要舔舔看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.81,0:06:40.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有電的味道哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.43,0:06:47.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.61,0:06:50.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.25,0:06:57.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時間該回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.64,0:07:04.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊  是認識的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.77,0:07:05.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.42,0:07:08.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢  就像是那女孩兄長般的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.67,0:07:10.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.58,0:07:13.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個學校的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.45,0:07:14.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼在這個時間還…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.30,0:07:17.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我想游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.89,0:07:20.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎是嗎  原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.70,0:07:22.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是暑假的最後一天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.26,0:07:25.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前也經常這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.79,0:07:28.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  對你這樣的調皮孩子是很寬大的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.62,0:07:30.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.22,0:07:32.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛結束
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.27,0:07:34.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C1  現在就出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.75,0:07:35.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C1  瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.32,0:07:36.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.42,0:07:38.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.70,0:07:39.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.85,0:07:42.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天是第一次游泳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.93,0:07:43.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他教我的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.20,0:07:47.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還真是多謝了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.25,0:07:50.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  你先出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.11,0:07:53.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面的人是不會傷害你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.55,0:08:02.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  淺羽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.62,0:08:06.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的整個暑假都和社長\N一起待在園原基地的後山啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.87,0:08:07.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.95,0:08:09.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是蠢蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.73,0:08:11.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.68,0:08:13.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.96,0:08:16.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你一定沒做作業吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.58,0:08:18.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要完全照抄哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.51,0:08:20.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點收起來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.73,0:08:23.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也別對社長太過於唯命是從了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.37,0:08:25.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得多點作為新聞社員的自覺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.97,0:08:28.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼什麼  真的去找UFO了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.61,0:08:29.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍到照片了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.08,0:08:30.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.80,0:08:33.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  園原基地是UFO基地的傳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.65,0:08:35.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從很久以前就在流傳了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.36,0:08:36.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是那樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.69,0:08:38.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是把隱形戰鬥機之類的給看錯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.15,0:08:42.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡不就是航空自衛軍和美空軍的據點嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.38,0:08:44.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照社長的原話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.12,0:08:48.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,園原基地附近目擊到的不明飛行物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.71,0:08:52.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說是Area Sonohara的Foo Fighter
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.71,0:08:52.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}（Area Sonohara：園原基地；Foo Fighter：幽靈戰鬥機）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.24,0:08:54.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Foo Fighter？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.90,0:08:57.21,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}（緊急時刻  此路禁止通行）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.00,0:08:56.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是幽靈戰鬥機
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.95,0:08:58.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本是二次世界大戰中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.87,0:09:02.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盟軍飛行員目擊到的不明飛行物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.83,0:09:06.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  當然  對於狂熱愛好者來說\N這也就是UFO的別名
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.90,0:09:08.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼認為呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.75,0:09:13.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最普遍的說法認為是\N園原基地在進行人造UFO發射
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.76,0:09:16.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回收墜落的UFO後  模仿其技術
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.59,0:09:18.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,製造出性能強大的飛機
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.64,0:09:20.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來  一旦發生戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.24,0:09:23.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種UFO戰鬥機不就會咻咻地飛來飛去？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.81,0:09:30.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會有啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.77,0:09:31.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.58,0:09:33.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會有的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:36.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最多也就是演習
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.89,0:09:39.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  防空避難演習？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.99,0:09:41.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  那真的有意義嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.63,0:09:45.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像…這次演習的主題是真實性呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.63,0:09:45.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(459,440)\fs24}Realism
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.85,0:09:46.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.51,0:09:59.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26}啊  好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.98,0:10:00.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26}萌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.58,0:10:03.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26}真讓人期待
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.88,0:10:07.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是伊里野 加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.38,0:10:28.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是班長中{\fn方正黑体_GBK}込{\r}真紀子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.70,0:10:30.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼不明白的地方都可以來找我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.90,0:10:32.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前住在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.46,0:10:33.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美國嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.13,0:10:35.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是和哥哥兩個人一起住的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.31,0:10:37.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人一起住在園原基地的居住區的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.90,0:10:39.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哥哥是做什麼的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.70,0:10:43.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  難道是飛行員？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.71,0:10:45.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  真厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.16,0:10:46.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英語一定很流利吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.01,0:10:48.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有幫忙你哥哥的工作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.86,0:11:02.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\an8}開學典禮馬上就要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.63,0:11:06.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\an8}請全校學生到體育館集合
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.06,0:11:08.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\an8}再重複一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.43,0:11:11.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\an8}開學典禮馬上就要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.74,0:11:16.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\an8}請全校學生到體育館集合…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.55,0:11:14.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  淺羽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.91,0:11:15.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,須藤同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.09,0:11:17.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和淺羽同學是認識的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.68,0:11:18.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  哪裡遇見的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.01,0:11:20.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是親戚？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.39,0:11:22.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  是以前的青梅竹馬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.51,0:11:25.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  滾開
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.24,0:11:29.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超級膽小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.31,0:11:32.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶穗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.57,0:11:34.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認識那女孩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.73,0:11:36.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.03,0:11:40.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此  那她又為什麼會那樣盯著你看啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.49,0:11:41.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪裡知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.49,0:11:42.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡遇見過？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.98,0:11:43.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.57,0:11:44.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.44,0:11:58.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒是說清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.72,0:11:59.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.63,0:12:03.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  淺羽  你沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.41,0:12:04.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臉色刷白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.67,0:12:05.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  淺羽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.92,0:12:06.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淺羽！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.52,0:12:10.40,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs17}起因責任人  椎名真由美
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.15,0:12:10.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好好吃過早飯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.78,0:12:13.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  但現在好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.49,0:12:14.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班級和姓名呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.14,0:12:17.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二年四班的淺羽直之
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.63,0:12:21.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二年四的…淺羽？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.36,0:12:24.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧  你就是那個淺羽同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.23,0:12:28.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  原來如此呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.64,0:12:35.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開學典禮已經開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.79,0:12:37.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.80,0:12:39.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.97,0:12:42.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是那位淺羽同學吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.87,0:12:44.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺不舒服是吧  沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.83,0:12:45.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有發燒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.65,0:12:47.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問  有什麼不對的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.04,0:12:50.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個吃了  稍微睡一下比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.81,0:13:04.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回想起來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:08.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個暑假也許並不是那麼糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.88,0:13:17.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,適可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.35,0:13:20.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對他使用了密斯特雞尾酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.35,0:13:20.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(386,439)\fs20}Mist Cocktail
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.54,0:13:22.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要做這種危險的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.70,0:13:24.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,植蟲也應該用其他更好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.59,0:13:26.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你放進了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.94,0:13:30.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我認為這是個無可厚非的選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.74,0:13:32.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然現在還不能斷言
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.25,0:13:33.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這應該是密斯特造成的幻覺重現
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.25,0:13:33.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(278,441)\fs24}mist
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.25,0:13:33.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(458,441)\fs24}flashback
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.76,0:13:37.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  我現在只是一個保健老師
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.87,0:13:39.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,密斯特的過量攝取
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.42,0:13:42.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我用紅藥水和喇叭商標來應付是不可能的！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.87,0:13:39.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(254,440)\fs20}mist
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.87,0:13:39.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(374,439)\fs20}overdose
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.61,0:13:45.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯絡不力的事情一定不要再發生了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.58,0:13:50.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\an8}暑假結束後
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.59,0:13:53.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\an8}大家往往都會鬆懈下來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.58,0:13:55.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\an8}本次的防空避難演習
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.95,0:13:58.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\an8}希望全員都要出席
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.27,0:13:58.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\an8}以上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.14,0:14:05.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開學典禮呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.63,0:14:08.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來的時候已經沒人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.14,0:14:12.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.52,0:14:13.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天早上啊  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.93,0:14:16.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\an8}啊  播報通知
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.18,0:14:19.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\an8}二年四班的伊里野加奈同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.13,0:14:22.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\an8}田中先生來電
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.75,0:14:24.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\an8}請你速到辦公室來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.90,0:14:26.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\an8}再重複一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.81,0:14:26.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電話？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.44,0:14:29.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\an8}二年四班的伊里野加奈同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.92,0:14:31.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\an8}田中先生來電
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.43,0:14:34.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\an8}請你速到辦公室來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.08,0:14:33.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我過去下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.22,0:14:35.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\an8}以上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.31,0:14:43.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之後可了不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.86,0:14:45.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中{\fn方正黑体_GBK}込{\r}她們都哭出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.70,0:14:48.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來轉校生留著鼻血離開了座位
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.45,0:14:51.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失口說錯話了的話道歉不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.25,0:14:53.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可她卻完全不認為自己有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.48,0:14:55.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不知道她當自己是什麼人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.34,0:15:01.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  吶  淺羽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.03,0:15:03.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天去社團嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.08,0:15:05.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.10,0:15:06.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野特派員
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.44,0:15:10.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.09,0:15:13.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淺羽特派員和須藤特派員
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.85,0:15:17.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疏忽了對如此優秀的人才的報告和勸誘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.30,0:15:18.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在是太鬆懈了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.29,0:15:20.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「勸誘」是指…？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.18,0:15:22.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.22,0:15:25.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們園原電波新聞社
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.18,0:15:27.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是將有如太陽系般廣大範疇的知識
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.64,0:15:32.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以宛如電波般的速度提供給\N讀者的少數精銳記者的團體
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.17,0:15:37.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天  特此歡迎伊里野特派員成為我社的新成員
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.44,0:15:40.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.80,0:15:43.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個…社長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.77,0:15:45.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  伊里野特派員
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.35,0:15:46.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放學後再來拜訪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.96,0:15:50.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有  請代我向自衛軍軍官的令兄問好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.37,0:15:51.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.23,0:15:55.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.27,0:16:03.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  把花留下了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.34,0:16:08.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淺羽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.02,0:16:12.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白癡似的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.67,0:16:22.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.78,0:16:24.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,6
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.76,0:16:26.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.72,0:16:28.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.29,0:16:33.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過時啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.20,0:16:34.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.04,0:16:36.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  這是社長你的提案啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.21,0:16:38.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7月號的新企劃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.94,0:16:41.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「畢業紀念冊裡的顯靈照」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.43,0:16:44.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們還在拘泥這種事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.54,0:16:45.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.41,0:16:50.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天6月24日是世界UFO日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.59,0:16:54.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1947年6月24日
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.17,0:16:56.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kenneth Arnold事件
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.39,0:16:58.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在華盛頓州的雷尼爾山
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.39,0:16:58.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(396,441)\fs24}rainier
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.02,0:17:01.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了最初的UFO目擊事件
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.57,0:17:02.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同一天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.02,0:17:06.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的UFO之夏  開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.67,0:17:17.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電…電話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.24,0:17:19.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你在打電話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.48,0:17:20.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不方便插話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.65,0:17:24.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛…剛才  對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.58,0:17:25.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇了一跳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.09,0:17:27.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我們的社長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.46,0:17:29.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在對園原基地進行取材
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.94,0:17:31.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是覺得如果拜託伊里野的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.25,0:17:33.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能夠幫上什麼忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.82,0:17:35.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  你哥哥是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.59,0:17:37.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.82,0:17:39.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是新聞社的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.50,0:17:41.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,須藤晶穗你認識嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.40,0:17:42.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.51,0:17:45.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然現在社員還只有社長和晶穗還有我三個人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.03,0:17:49.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.88,0:17:53.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果伊里野也加入的話就有4個人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.54,0:18:00.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我比較忙…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.29,0:18:09.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.85,0:18:16.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演習啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.39,0:18:19.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊  今天有演習
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.34,0:18:20.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防空避難…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.60,0:18:26.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.82,0:18:28.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.97,0:18:31.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.89,0:18:36.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊急事態下的防爆姿勢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.80,0:18:37.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是演習
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.39,0:18:39.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.71,0:18:41.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了因為是演習嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.89,0:18:42.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.00,0:19:03.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.06,0:19:11.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通行密碼已變更
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.06,0:19:11.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(281,441)\fs24}route code
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.38,0:19:14.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隔層的密碼封鎖完成
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.20,0:19:17.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和外界回路進行物理性隔絕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.78,0:19:19.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關…關上了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.06,0:19:19.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}通行密碼已變更
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.09,0:19:22.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.56,0:19:27.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的警報只是演習
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.89,0:19:28.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防空演習的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.10,0:19:30.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿著  以防萬一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.52,0:19:33.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能會闖進來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.25,0:19:36.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是演習  不是戰爭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.63,0:19:40.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭在1947年就已經開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.76,0:19:42.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是大家都沒有發覺而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.39,0:19:46.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1947年…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.87,0:19:49.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kenneth Arnold事件
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.08,0:20:08.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.85,0:20:09.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接通了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.79,0:20:10.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  淺羽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.54,0:20:11.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  是我  榎本
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.70,0:20:13.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…請問你找誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.88,0:20:17.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？什麼嘛  昨天晚上在游泳池見過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.34,0:20:19.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道我那時候沒自報家門嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.66,0:20:21.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.53,0:20:24.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這裡也在想辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.94,0:20:27.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你們還得在那裡待上一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.18,0:20:29.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一會兒算是…！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.47,0:20:33.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換伊里野？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.33,0:20:39.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.90,0:20:41.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.95,0:20:46.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來的確是演習呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.14,0:20:50.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.90,0:20:55.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是空襲就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.13,0:20:57.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.37,0:21:00.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家全都死掉就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.64,0:21:02.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸掉就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.68,0:21:10.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.32,0:21:13.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野的遊戲機？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.32,0:21:17.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}mission Barrier Combat Air Patrol{\r}\N任務  阻攔式空中戰鬥巡邏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.67,0:21:20.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以玩一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.24,0:21:26.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了來了  右邊右邊  向右散開
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.24,0:21:26.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(475,439)\fs20}break
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.12,0:21:27.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.48,0:21:29.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反了  不是那邊  反了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.52,0:21:31.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快了  就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.47,0:21:33.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了有了有了  B鍵  B鍵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.53,0:21:34.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快按快按  FOX
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.03,0:21:36.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行  太近了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.46,0:21:37.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快按  快按快按
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.69,0:21:44.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？  結束了…？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.50,0:21:47.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.67,0:21:54.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.47,0:21:56.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.27,0:22:00.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.95,0:22:01.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是伊里野嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.71,0:22:03.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榎本先生  喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.20,0:22:03.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野流鼻血了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.91,0:22:07.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在玩遊戲  然後伊里野突然倒下一動不動了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.08,0:22:07.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全身在抽搐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.06,0:22:08.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淺羽  冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.38,0:22:10.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.47,0:22:11.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有意識嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.04,0:22:13.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.01,0:22:14.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜下來  聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.28,0:22:17.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在伊里野大腿內側用力捏一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.74,0:22:19.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看她有沒有反應
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.14,0:22:19.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.03,0:22:26.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有動  沒有動啊  怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.98,0:22:27.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.81,0:22:29.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間緊迫  只能拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.31,0:22:32.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊里野攜帶的物品裡有張灰色的卡片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.25,0:22:35.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.50,0:22:41.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡找貼有「P-3KI」標簽的箱子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.58,0:22:42.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.60,0:22:46.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它注射到伊里野的心臟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.52,0:22:48.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快做
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.45,0:22:50.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脫下內衣後就能看到胸口的標記
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.32,0:22:51.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸口…？！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.42,0:22:52.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不是害羞的時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.48,0:22:55.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到小學六年級都還和妹妹\N一起洗澡的是哪裡的哪個傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.73,0:23:01.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會知道那件事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.86,0:23:03.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.52,0:23:30.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徹底成名人了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.67,0:23:31.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.80,0:23:33.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.57,0:23:34.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.56,0:23:35.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.43,0:23:36.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.14,0:23:36.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.94,0:23:38.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼叫「什麼啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.90,0:23:43.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.79,0:23:45.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西久保  花村
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.44,0:23:46.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.80,0:23:50.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電這東西  舔上去會有味道嗎


